<br>
Fire and Fury without Xadria is like EQ without Firiona Vie =-(.<br>
<br>
I don't know what could have caused you to leave.  I am very sad to see you go.  Xadria and Entity are two names I have associated with Fire and Fury ever since I was training orc pawns to Kelethin guards.  My awe and wonder over the powerful guild known as Fire and Fury started back then.<br>
<br>
